title: Warwick double Q Bug
body:
I played a ranked 3v3 as Fiora vs a Warwick toplane. He Q'd me and it dealt double damage, first i thought that it was legit. But I watched the replay and he healed twice  ~40 health + he lost 100 Mana (Warwick Q lvl 1 costs 50)

I uploaded the recorded content to youtube, here is a link.
